{"tid":2320341,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"E罩杯AV女優爆瘦！變「健身魔人」狂啪啪　她曝殘忍真相","createTime":"2020-12-10T17:35:31.000Z","updateTime":"2020-12-11T05:16:20.000Z","uid":16659,"like":21,"dislike":78,"uniUserReply":27,"replies":[{"pid":"c3c83e4342a8e07d776bb1454c46f122fa94d26a","tid":2320341,"uid":16659,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-10T17:35:31.000Z","msg":"日本AV女優七海蒂娜（七海ティナ），除擁有34E豐滿胸圍，更以一身精壯肌肉成為特色。近日她在Twitter曝光6年前擔任偶像時期的舊照，相較現在整整胖了20公斤，體型相差甚大，引發粉絲討論。而這樣的轉變，全來自兒時的霸凌陰影，讓她下定決心改變 !<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://attach.setn.com/newsimages/2020/12/10/2929297-PH.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fattach.setn.com%2Fnewsimages%2F2020%2F12%2F10%2F2929297-PH.jpg&h=2a27f1c4&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n▲日本AV女優七海蒂娜（七海ティナ），除擁有34E豐滿胸圍，更以一身精壯肌肉成為特色。（合成圖／翻攝自七海蒂娜推特）<br />\n<br />\n現年27歲的七海蒂娜，6年前以名古屋地下偶像出道成為寫真女星，隨後又加入成員多為AV女優的女團「惠比壽麝香葡萄」，去年正式成為AV女優，並以健美的體態及E罩杯逆天身材擄獲大批粉絲喜愛。近日她在Twitter曝光多張偶像時期的照片，只見當時的她雙頰、體型臃腫，浮腫的膝蓋及粗壯大腿更顯份量，與現在精實模樣判若兩人。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://attach.setn.com/newsimages/2020/12/10/2929291-PH.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fattach.setn.com%2Fnewsimages%2F2020%2F12%2F10%2F2929291-PH.jpg&h=c2923b87&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n▲▼七海蒂娜日前在Twitter曝光多張偶像時期的照片，只見當時的她雙頰、體型臃腫，與現在精實模樣判若兩人。（圖／翻攝自七海蒂娜推特）<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://attach.setn.com/newsimages/2020/12/10/2929289-PH.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fattach.setn.com%2Fnewsimages%2F2020%2F12%2F10%2F2929289-PH.jpg&h=e3f496ad&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n事實上，七海蒂娜日前曾透露，自學生時期就因微胖身材遭霸凌，直至拍攝寫真時仍擺脫不了被嫌胖的噩夢，讓她痛定思痛，決心以健身和調整飲食展開減肥之路，而這一減成功剷除20公斤肥肉，不只身材變得精壯，就連五官都顯得精緻許多。七海蒂娜現在除了拍攝AV外，仍不定期參加健身比賽，維持完美身材。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://attach.setn.com/newsimages/2020/12/10/2929293-PH.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fattach.setn.com%2Fnewsimages%2F2020%2F12%2F10%2F2929293-PH.jpg&h=9afe8246&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n▲▼七海蒂娜現在除了拍攝AV外，仍不定期參加健身比賽，維持完美身材。（圖／翻攝自七海蒂娜推特）<br />\n<img src=\"https://attach.setn.com/newsimages/2020/12/09/2927575-PH.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fattach.setn.com%2Fnewsimages%2F2020%2F12%2F09%2F2927575-PH.jpg&h=96b66e58&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"68623b90466db421417324662a22e28185fb1da6","tid":2320341,"uid":344609,"like":2,"dislike":14,"score":-12,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-12-10T17:37:25.000Z","msg":"犀利咁佢瘦咗之後仲係咪大波？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/surprise.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6175f6b8edf31e598c2b65cffa12c797fd62c230","tid":2320341,"uid":16659,"like":3,"dislike":7,"score":-4,"quote":{"pid":"68623b90466db421417324662a22e28185fb1da6","tid":2320341,"uid":344609,"like":2,"dislike":14,"score":-12,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-12-10T17:37:25.000Z","msg":"犀利咁佢瘦咗之後仲係咪大波？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/surprise.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-12-10T17:40:07.000Z","msg":"好似係<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"23c04f593781e434076dc7721ae9984488e87c7f","tid":2320341,"uid":382485,"like":47,"dislike":1,"score":46,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-10T17:40:10.000Z","msg":"整咗幾多樣<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2145026c20374e181605c02013df42b5ce02b81c","tid":2320341,"uid":308570,"like":53,"dislike":3,"score":50,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-12-10T17:40:13.000Z","msg":"做pr做到咁夜都要出post<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e1b1e642ae261526b959abead02f27453ab17c78","tid":2320341,"uid":344609,"like":3,"dislike":1,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"6175f6b8edf31e598c2b65cffa12c797fd62c230","tid":2320341,"uid":16659,"like":3,"dislike":7,"score":-4,"quote":{"pid":"68623b90466db421417324662a22e28185fb1da6","tid":2320341,"uid":344609,"like":2,"dislike":14,"score":-12,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-12-10T17:37:25.000Z","msg":"犀利咁佢瘦咗之後仲係咪大波？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/surprise.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-12-10T17:40:07.000Z","msg":"好似